1
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:22,360
Today I tried making basil stir-fry.

2
00:00:22,392 --> 00:00:24,360
I saw you always liked eating it with Mom.

3
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:26,000
Give it a try, Dad.

4
00:00:36,504 --> 00:00:38,024
Eat up, okay?

5
00:00:41,330 --> 00:00:42,288
Is it delicious?

6
00:00:46,930 --> 00:00:48,328
Try some, Dad.

7
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,080
Tell me what you think.

8
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,296
If you like it, I’ll make it for you again.

9
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,384
I really miss Mom, don’t you?

10
00:00:54,992 --> 00:00:56,990
I should have made this for her sooner.

11
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:00,600
So… Do you like it, Dad?

12
00:01:00,632 --> 00:01:01,560
I’m not hungry!

13
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,072
I’m going up to my room.

14
00:01:03,390 --> 00:01:04,648
Dad, what’s wrong with you?!

15
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,104
You’ve been like this since this morning.

16
00:01:07,512 --> 00:01:09,510
Why are you taking your work stress out on me?

17
00:01:10,688 --> 00:01:12,690
We only have each other left, Dad.

18
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:15,128
If you know I’m stressed, then just stay away from me!

19
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:18,016
How can I not care about you?

20
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,816
You’re my dad.

21
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,104
If Mom were still here, she would probably…

22
00:01:24,128 --> 00:01:26,128
STOP! I’m sick of this!

23
00:01:32,264 --> 00:01:34,792
I know you’ve always looked down on me.

24
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:37,920
You think I’m incompetent.

25
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:41,216
All you ever cared about was your mom.

26
00:01:42,112 --> 00:01:46,464
I know you two always looked down on me behind my back!

27
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:48,728
What are you talking about?!

28
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,312
Mom and I loved you more than anything.

29
00:01:51,352 --> 00:01:53,600
You loved us too, didn't you?

30
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:58,136
I never loved either of you.

31
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:22,944
P’Chat..

32
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:54,864
Leave me alone!

33
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:57,320
No, I’m going to stay right here.

34
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,624
I have no one left, Ran.

35
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,800
It’s okay, P’Chat. I’m here.

36
00:03:06,832 --> 00:03:12,224
If he doesn’t love Mom, and he doesn’t love me... then why did he let me be born?!

37
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:14,960
P’Chat, it’s okay.

38
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,792
I’m right here.

39
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:32,280
P’Chat... you’re going to be okay.

40
00:03:39,650 --> 00:03:40,656
Everything is fine.

41
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:51,104
From now on, no matter what happens,

42
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:55,600
I’ll be by your side.

43
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,336
I will never betray you.

44
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:03,656
I promise.

45
00:04:12,850 --> 00:04:15,576
So, it’s okay, alright?

46
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,784
You have me.

47
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:28,784
I only have you...

48
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:32,496
and just having you is enough.

49
00:06:59,530 --> 00:07:01,568
6 Years Later

50
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,016
Gorgeous!

51
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:25,648
She’s not just gorgeous; she’s brilliant.

52
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:28,952
I heard the US branch K’Chat is managing has grown so much it’s already broken even.

53
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:30,272
My schedule is cleared for this afternoon, right?

54
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:32,208
All set, ma'am.

55
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:34,480
Good morning, Khun Chat!

56
00:07:34,512 --> 00:07:35,352
Hello.

57
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:40,176
Wow... we might be getting a new President this year.

58
00:07:40,208 --> 00:07:41,984
You mean a father-daughter showdown for the top spot?

59
00:07:43,110 --> 00:07:46,000
We'll just have to see who stays and who goes!

60
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,224
Gossiping!

61
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:52,256
K’Wichai, our stock price has been dropping recently because of the clip...

62
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:55,496
Spit it out, Sira.

63
00:07:57,300 --> 00:08:00,512
You were going to say the leaked clip of me at the bar, weren't you?

64
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:07,480
Damn it! It’s nothing more than high-society gossip.

65
00:08:07,528 --> 00:08:10,224
Once the buzz dies down, the stock will bounce back on its own.

66
00:08:10,592 --> 00:08:12,590
Now... does anyone else have anything to add?

67
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:13,848
I do.

68
00:08:21,850 --> 00:08:22,960
When did you get back?

69
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:24,320
This morning.

70
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,672
I came straight here as soon as my flight landed.

71
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:34,624
Um... so, Dad, where would you like me to sit?

72
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:38,424
Over there. Go.

73
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:17,408
I hope that next time, you can arrange a better seat for me than that.

74
00:09:27,530 --> 00:09:28,984
Now, which point were we discussing?

75
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:30,392
Please, continue.

76
00:09:31,110 --> 00:09:33,616
And how are things going with the US branch, K’Chat?

77
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:39,480
Sales have doubled since we partnered with local suppliers.

78
00:09:39,528 --> 00:09:44,304
We're planning to expand into Europe and Canada later this year.

79
00:09:48,768 --> 00:09:51,408
Excellent, My daughter is all grown up now.

80
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:56,848
Yes, I’m 24 now.

81
00:09:57,816 --> 00:09:59,820
You’ve worked hard for a long time.

82
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:04,568
From now on, I’ll take over the business for you.
